==Korean==
===Noun===
'''벌''' '''beol'''
#(open area of land) a [[field]], a [[plain]]
#a set (of clothes)
#:한복 한 벌을 ''hanbok han beoreur'' A set of '''[[hanbok]]'''. 
#a [[bee]] (or a [[wasp]], [[hornet]] etc) 
#:벌에 쏘이다 beore ssoida. ''Be stung by a bee''. 
#:''Related terms'': [[꿀벌]] (kkulbeor), [[honey bee]]; [[말발]] (malbar), [[hornet]]; [[호박벌]] (hobakbeor), [[carpenter bee]]
#([[罰]]) punishment, penalty
#:''Related terms'': [[벌하다]] (beolhada) to punish; [[벌받다]] (beolbatda), to be punished

